Hi Ken,

In the address bar (also location bar or URL bar) when I type:
*about:addons *or *about:plugins*

I can see the version of flash being used by Iceweasel and in my case it
is: *Shockwave Flash 11.2 r202. *

And in Chrome when I type:
*chrome://plugins/*

it shows me Adobe Flash Player* - Version: 16.0.0.305*
* Shockwave Flash 16.0 r0*

So am guessing Ice-weasel is unable to play the stream due to the flash
version not being the very latest as in chrome.

